  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to mpv</title>

    <para>
      <application>mpv</application> is a free media player for the command
line. It supports a wide variety of media file formats, audio and video
codecs, and subtitle types.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&mpv-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
